```mermaid
graph TD
    subgraph Frontend[Frontend Layer]
        webapp(Next.js Web App)
    end

    subgraph Backend[Backend Layer]
        api(FastAPI Server)
        worker(Celery Worker)
    end

    subgraph Database[Data Layer]
        postgres[(PostgreSQL)]
        redis[(Redis Cache & Queue)]
    end

    subgraph AI[AI & External Services]
        openai(Azure OpenAI)
        pinecone[(Pinecone Vector DB)]
        blob(Azure Blob Storage)
    end

    webapp -->|REST API| api
    
    api -->|Async ORM| postgres
    api -->|Pub/Sub| redis
    api -->|Dispatch Tasks| worker
    worker -->|Listen for Tasks| redis

    api -->|Embeddings / Chat| openai
    api -->|Vector Search| pinecone
    api -->|Upload Files| blob
    
    worker -->|Async Embedding| openai
    worker -->|Index Docs| pinecone
```
